  "instructions": [
    "in a large saucepan, heat the coconut oil over medium heat.",
    "add the grated ginger and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "add the almonds and cook for an additional 2 minutes, until lightly toasted.",
    "add the pitted medjool dates, allspice, cinnamon, and nutmeg. stir to combine.",
    "cook for 5 minutes, until the dates are tender.",
    "stir in the maple syrup, soy sauce, and crushed candy canes.",
    "reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "serve warm, garnished with additional crushed candy canes if desired."
